graph { flow: south; }

# README architecture — deployment side-channel.
#
# newtlab puts SONiC VMs on the network (creates QEMU processes, wires
# socket links) and exits. specs feed newtron-server at load time.
# Neither path runs during normal operation — these are setup/lifecycle
# concerns.

[ specs ]       --> [ newtron-server ]
[ newtlab CLI ] --> { label: deploy, wire; } [ SONiC VM ]
